		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			        &nbsp; 300lb Fish -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game hold L2+R2+L1+R1 THEN PRESS UP,DOWN,LEFT,CIRCLE</font>&nbsp;
			       <br>&nbsp; Larger fish -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, then hold Select and press L2, R2, R1, Up</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Bonus levels -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Successfully complete challenge mode to unlock two more levels</font>&nbsp;
			       <br>&nbsp; Bonus lures -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">A new lure will become available for each level in challenge mode that is completed</font>&nbsp;
			       <br>&nbsp; Simple to get Super Big fish -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game and hold select than press L2,R2,R1 and up</font>&nbsp;
			       <br>&nbsp; Get over 300oz fish -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Press pause then hold select and press L2 R2 L1 R1 UP DOWN</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
